  "detailed_description": "<strong><br>A rabbit named Hop braves the tutorial temple to find the secret to everlasting life. Unbeknownst to him, the secret is the eternal afterlife. He dies, goes to Heaven, gets sent to Hell, reincarnates and journeys through multiple lives to reach the goals.<br>Dodge is a skull that's been trapped in the garden of Heaven for thousands of years. He begs Hop to hit the red switch to free him and when he does get free, he destroys Heaven. Hop only has one option to continue, team up with this unlikely ally to find a way back to Heaven. Dodge on the other hand is looking for his bones.<br><br>opDo.<br><br>  </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965680/extras/00bf0b0ce2745e8050389febe082e6d0.poster.avif?t=1719105277\" width=800 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965680/extras/00bf0b0ce2745e8050389febe082e6d0.webm?t=1719105277\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965680/extras/00bf0b0ce2745e8050389febe082e6d0.mp4?t=1719105277\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2></strong><br><br><strong>Top Down AND 3D platforming</strong><br>Hop around on the back plane as Hop OR <br>Jump and weave in the 3D platforming mode as Dodge<br><br><strong>50+ Base Levels to play through</strong><br>Solve puzzles, Avoid traps and obstacles, and explore 50+ different challenging levels<br><br><strong>Create and Share your own levels</strong><br>Using an in-game editor, build levels and contraptions to your heart's desire then share those creations online using Steam Workshop.<br><br><strong>Multiplayer</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965680/extras/aadb58a232ad79fcede5e6c86cca921f.poster.avif?t=1719105277\" width=472 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965680/extras/aadb58a232ad79fcede5e6c86cca921f.webm?t=1719105277\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965680/extras/aadb58a232ad79fcede5e6c86cca921f.mp4?t=1719105277\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Play the same level as your friend and see each other as ghosts and interact!<br>Or create an editor lobby and have your friends join you and create levels together.<br><br>If you don't get the game, Hop will get hit by car :c<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965680/extras/9f3b5498f0620f230e3c73aefbdcf800.poster.avif?t=1719105277\" width=426 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965680/extras/9f3b5498f0620f230e3c73aefbdcf800.webm?t=1719105277\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1965680/extras/9f3b5498f0620f230e3c73aefbdcf800.mp4?t=1719105277\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
